#Author: persist
#Abstract: how to install docker on ubuntu

# get the newest docker installation package

``` bash
$ wget -qO- https://get.docker.com/ | sh
```


# check whether docker has been successfully installed

``` bash
$ sudo docker run hello-world
```

# Note
	see https://github.com/widuu/chinese_docker/blob/master/installation/ubuntu.md  to learn more details

## start docker daemon

``` bash
$ sudo docker daemon
```

``` bash
$ sudo dockerd
```

``` bash
$ sudo service docker start
```
